HEADWORD: Granolithic
<hw>Gran`o*lith"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>granum</ets> a grain (or E. <ets>granite</ets>) + <ets>-lith +
-ic</ets>.]</ety> <def>A kind of hard artificial stone, used for
pavements.</def>⟦br⟧
